# SSCS CI-only tooling — hash-pinned closure, INSTALLED SEPARATELY from the
# runtime/build closure (requirements.lock) so CI tool installs are pinned by
# hash (Scorecard Pinned-Dependencies). Compile with:
#   pip-compile --generate-hashes --output-file=requirements-citools.lock requirements-citools.in
# These tools never ship to users; they run only in CI jobs.
